    <h1>Thadeus Siwecki</h1>
    <p>I curently live in Pontiac, Illinois</p>
    <p>I am married to my wife, Beckie, and we have four daughters. Our oldest daughter is 33 years old and our youngest daughter is 26 years old. We have three gandsons and one granddaughter. We are raising our two youngest grandson's who are seven and nine.</p>
    <p>I grew up ouside San Antonio, Texas, and joined the US Marine Corps when I graduated high school. I did six years active duty and went into the Army National Guard. I retired after my thied depolyment with 28 years of service.</p>
    <p>I began a career in law enforcement in 1990 and retired in 2018 as a police lieutenant/division commander. I am currently a high school paraprofessional working with at risk youth.</p>    
